ion.\n\u003c/p\u003e","files":null},{"type":3,"author":{"id":"6d59fc378929d99368e023bcfc49aacae1e68aad"},"timestamp":1290646863,"metadata":{"github-id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDM1MDMyNTc=","github-url":"https://github.com/parrot/parrot/issues/468#issuecomment-3503257"},"message":"\u003cp\u003e\nI like that idea.\n\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\nBut the main point, implementation details apart, is to decide if we want to change the current behavior, and in that case add a deprecation notice and document the new one.\n\u003c/p\u003e","files":null}]}